OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after Bianca
OL,4,CWilliams stop and search set to appeal
OL,6,FTwo police officers sacked for lying
OL,7,Fafter saying that they could smell
OL,8,Fcannabis during a stop and search of
OL,9,FBritish athlete Bianca Williams and
OL,10,Fher partner will have an appeal heard
OL,11,Fin October.
OL,13,FFormer Met Pcs Jonathan Clapham and
OL,14,FSam Franks were dismissed in October
OL,15,Flast year after a disciplinary panel
OL,16,Ffound they had lied about smelling the
OL,17,Fdrug when they pulled over Olympic
OL,18,Fsprinter Ricardo Dos Santos and his
OL,19,Fpartner Williams on July 4 2020.
