OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after Bianca
OL,4,CWilliams stop and search set to appeal
OL,6,FThe police followed the athletes as
OL,7,Fthey drove back from training to their
OL,8,Fwest London home with their baby son,
OL,9,Fthen three months old, in the back
OL,10,Fseat of their Mercedes.
OL,12,FOfficers handcuffed the couple and
OL,13,Fthey were searched on suspicion of
OL,14,Fhaving drugs and weapons but nothing
OL,15,Fwas found.
OL,17,FThe force came under heavy criticism
OL,18,Fafter footage of the stop was posted
OL,19,Fon social media, showing a distressed
OL,20,FWilliams who was concerned about being
OL,21,Fseparated from her baby.
