OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after Bianca
OL,4,CWilliams stop and search set to appeal
OL,6,FMisconduct panel chairwoman Chiew Yin
OL,7,FJones said Clapham and Franks' conduct
OL,8,Fhad breached standards of professional
OL,9,Fbehaviour in respect of honesty and
OL,10,Fintegrity and this amounted to gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct. They were then sacked.
OL,13,FAfter the hearing, Deputy Assistant
OL,14,FCommissioner Matt Ward said: "While
OL,15,Fthe panel accepted the officers'
OL,16,Fversion of events in most matters,
OL,17,Fincluding that their decisions were
OL,18,Fnot motivated by ethnicity, it found
OL,19,Fthat PC Clapham and PC Franks lied
OL,20,Fabout smelling drugs on stopping the
OL,21,Fvehicle.
