OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after Bianca
OL,4,CWilliams stop and search set to appeal
OL,6,F"Honesty and integrity are at the core
OL,7,Fof policing and, as the panel has
OL,8,Fconcluded, there can be no place in
OL,9,Fthe Met for officers who do not uphold
OL,10,Fthese values."
OL,12,FIn the wake of their dismissal, an
OL,13,Fonline appeal raised more than
OL,14,F#150,000 for the officers.
OL,16,FThe Police Appeals Tribunal, which
OL,17,Fhears appeals against findings of
OL,18,Fgross misconduct involving police
OL,19,Fofficers, will hear their case on
OL,20,FOctober 3 and 4.
